title: Aelafat Zemarie 2025
description: A large-scale Ethiopian Orthodox Tewahedo spiritual gathering and choir movement that gained significant popularity throughout 2025. It is characterized by mass choir performances involving thousands of vocalists, often organized by the Ethiopian Eunuch Generation (የኢትዮጵያዊው ጃንደረባ ትውልድ).
